  "title": "🍗 CRAVE - STORE MANAGER",
  "description": "<h3>🔥 WE’RE HIRING: STORE MANAGER 🔥</h3>\n<p><strong>Join the Crave family — where great food meets great people!</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Are you a natural leader with a passion for local flavours and creating awesome customer experiences? Crave is looking for motivated and hands-on Store Managers to lead our team and deliver Singapore’s favourite Nasi Lemak with pride! 🇸🇬</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<h3>What You’ll Do:</h3>\n<p>🥢 Lead and motivate your team to deliver excellent service and quality food<br>\n📈 Drive daily sales and store performance targets<br>\n🍗 Oversee store operations — from food prep to cash handling and inventory<br>\n🍳 Maintain high food quality, hygiene, and safety standards<br>\n🌟 Train and develop team members to reach their full potential</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<h3><strong>What We’re Looking For:</strong></h3>\n<p>✔️ At least 1–2 years of experience in F&amp;B or retail leadership<br>\n✔️ Strong team management and communication skills<br>\n✔️ Hands-on attitude — not afraid to jump in when needed<br>\n✔️ Passion for great food and service<br>\n✔️ Able to work shifts, weekends &amp; public holidays</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<h3><strong>Why Join Crave?</strong></h3>\n<p>✨ Career advancement opportunities<br>\n✨ Attractive incentives &amp; performance bonuses<br>\n✨ Supportive team culture<br>\n✨ Staff meals (you’ll never crave elsewhere again 😉)</p>\n<p>✨ Able to follow standard operating procedure, ensuring accuracy in a timely manner</p>\n<p>✨ Willing to work shifts, F&amp;B hours</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><em>*Terms and conditions apply.</em></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Ready to lead a team that serves happiness — one plate at a time?</p>\n<p><br>\n👉 <strong>Apply now and grow your career with Crave!</strong></p>",
